author: Doug P.
title: Uh oh! Cher tells opponents of Trump’s SCOTUS nominee to ‘GET OVER IT,’ #Resist crowd rebels
text:
Uh oh! Cher tells opponents of Trump’s SCOTUS nominee to ‘GET OVER IT,’ #Resist crowd rebels Posted at 5:03 pm on February 1, 2017 by Doug P. Share on Facebook Share on Twitter 
Cher tweeted today that Dems should choose their battles, and the nomination of Neil Gorsuch isn’t one of them: SCOTUS IS A DONE DEAL,GET OVER IT‼️WE’LL HATE HIS DECISIONS,BUT ITS TRUMPS RIGHT.FIGHT 4THINGS U CAN IMPACT https://t.co/QprrSvitKQ 
Now she did it! The #Resist crowd has been triggered: @cher Cher…….rethink this 
— Bile Cube (@BileCube) February 1, 2017 I disagree…Dems always roll over…resist!!! https://t.co/QhQv4yWywL 
— lyndy schaefer (@lyndy1115) February 1, 2017 @cher Um, no. It's NOT a done deal. And, it's a disaster for us. So, no giving in.
